# React components

## Conventions

- Functional components; export default at bottom
- Wrap sections with `SectionWrapper(Component, "sectionId")` unless Skills uses custom wrapper
- Animations: import variants from `src/utils/motion.js` (`fadeIn`, `textVariant`, `staggerContainer`)
- Shared layout classes: `src/styles.js`

## Section IDs (nav targets)

- `about`, `skills`, `experience`, `work` (projects), `education`, `github`, `contact`
- Keep `navLinks` in constants aligned with SectionWrapper ids

## Performance

- Lazy-load heavy 3D (`ComputersCanvas`) with `React.lazy` + `Suspense`
- Avoid new `console.log` in production paths

## Do not

- Re-enable unused canvas exports (`EarthCanvas`, `BallCanvas`, `StarsCanvas`) without user request
- Add `Tech.jsx` stub to App without implementation
